Interface ItsNatDroidDocumentTemplate

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ItsNatDocumentTemplate, ItsNatUserData, MarkupTemplate

    public interface ItsNatDroidDocumentTemplate
extends ItsNatDocumentTemplate
    Represents a document (page) template of Android layout. Concrete documents are created using this template.
